### FastVocab API - Topics Management Test
@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001/api
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Get all topics (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/topics
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 2. Get visible topics only (Student)
GET {{baseUrl}}/topics/visible
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 3. Get topic by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/topics/1
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 4. Create new topic
POST {{baseUrl}}/topics
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Business English",
  "vnText": "Tiếng Anh Thương Mại",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/business-english.jpg"
}

### 5. Create another topic
POST {{baseUrl}}/topics
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Technology & IT",
  "vnText": "Công Nghệ & CNTT",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/technology.jpg"
}

### 6. Update topic (replace ID with actual ID from create response)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/topics/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Business English Advanced",
  "vnText": "Tiếng Anh Thương Mại Nâng Cao",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/business-english-advanced.jpg",
  "isHiding": false
}

### 7. Toggle topic visibility (Hide)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/topics/1/visibility
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 8. Toggle topic visibility again (Show)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/topics/1/visibility
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 9. Delete topic (Soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/topics/1

### 10. Try to get deleted topic (Should return error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/topics/1
Accept: {{contentType}}

